title: Will Cooper Rush Dak Back?
description:
Jalen and Jacoby discuss the Cowboys win over the Giants on Monday night football, and they discuss the biggest storylines to come out of NBA media day including LeBron's 20th season, Kevin Durant returning to the Nets, and Kyrie turning down 100 million to remain unvaccinated. All that and much more!
